### check Debezium Connect status
GET http://localhost:8083/

### list registered connectors
GET http://localhost:8083/connectors

### register v3 connector — CDC on operations table
### Debezium reads the WAL and publishes to topic: cdc.public.operations
POST http://localhost:8083/connectors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "v3-operations-cdc-connector",
  "config": {
    "connector.class": "io.debezium.connector.postgresql.PostgresConnector",
    "database.hostname": "postgres_db",
    "database.port": "5432",
    "database.dbname": "operations_db",
    "database.user": "postgres",
    "database.password": "postgres",
    "topic.prefix": "cdc",
    "table.include.list": "public.operations",
    "plugin.name": "pgoutput",
    "slot.name": "v3_operations_slot",
    "publication.name": "v3_operations_pub",
    "snapshot.mode": "never",
    "key.converter": "org.apache.kafka.connect.json.JsonConverter",
    "key.converter.schemas.enable": "false",
    "value.converter": "org.apache.kafka.connect.json.JsonConverter",
    "value.converter.schemas.enable": "false"
  }
}

### check connector status
GET http://localhost:8083/connectors/v3-operations-cdc-connector/status

### delete connector
DELETE http://localhost:8083/connectors/v3-operations-cdc-connector
